thread.title: 'Wonder Woman' stumbles, 'Get Out' surprises at Oscar nominations

title: 'Wonder Woman' stumbles, 'Get Out' surprises at Oscar nominations
text:
'Wonder Woman' stumbles, 'Get Out' surprises at Oscar nominations 4:28am EST - 01:12 
Fan favorite 'Wonder Woman,' one of the biggest box office hits of 2017, misses out on any Oscar recognition, in a year when nominations pour in for other movies about women and made by women. Jane Ross reports.
